**Story**

Once upon a time, there was a crocodile learning to read and his best friend was a monkey. 
The monkey was a coder and made an app to help him learn to read
The name of the app was Monkey Chunky.
It broke the word's into chunks and played the phonics for you.
The crocodile used it very much.
Until the crocodile and monkey got into a fight.
The monkey then shut down the app and the crocodile ate the monkey.
The End.
